 Line]] to/from {{STN|Karakida}}</ref>\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#cdf; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#beb; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#fbb; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#bfb; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#ebe; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|{{Plainlist|\n* {{JRLS|JY}} [[Yamanote Line]] (JY25)\n* {{JRLS|JK}} [[Keihin-T\u014dhoku Line]] (JK20)\n* {{JRLS|JO}} [[Yokosuka Line]] (JO17)\n* {{JRLS|JT}} [[Tokaido Line]] (JT03)\n* [[File:Shinkansen jrc.svg|17px|\u25a0]] [[Tokaido Shinkansen]]\n* {{KQLS}} [[Keiky\u016b Main Line]] (KK01)\n}}\n| rowspan=\"10\" style=\"width:1em; text-align:center; line-height:300%;\" |Two\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Minato, Tokyo|Minato]]\n|rowspan=\"13\" style=\"text-align:center; width:1em; line-height:200%;\"|Tokyo\n|-\n|{{STN|Shimbashi}}<br>{{JRSN|JT|02|tlc=SMB|size=40}}\n|\u65b0\u6a4b\n|style=\"text-align:right;\"|4.9\n|style=\"text-align:right;\"|7.7\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#cdf; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#beb; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#fbb; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#bfb; text-align:center;\"|'''\uff5c'''\n|style=\"width:1em; background:#ebe; text-align:center;\"|'''\uff5c'''\n|{{Plainlist|\n* {{JRLS|JY}} Yamanote Line (JY29)\n* {{JRLS|JK}} Keihin-T\u014dhoku Line (JK24)\n* {{JRLS|JO}} Yokosuka Line (JO18)\n* {{TSLS|G}} Tokyo Metro Ginza Line (G-08)\n* {{TSLS|A}} [[Toei Asakusa Line]] (A-10)\n* [[Yurikamome]] (U-01)\n}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{STN|Tokyo}}<br> {{JRSNH|tlc=TYO|span=2|size=40}}{{JRSN|JT|01|seq=1|size=40}}{{JRSN|JU|01|seq=2|size=40}}{{JRSNF}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"|\u6771\u4eac\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|1.9\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|5.8\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em; background:#cdf; text-align:center;\"|\u25cf\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em; background:#beb; text